  "detailed_description": "What is your happy place?<br>Maybe it's a bedroom. A calm place in the open. Your bathroom. Or maybe... your personal computer?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/c46c730b9d29a21ca216df47baed1021.poster.avif?t=1730629913\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/c46c730b9d29a21ca216df47baed1021.webm?t=1730629913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/c46c730b9d29a21ca216df47baed1021.mp4?t=1730629913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>During times of need, a programmer developed a virtual cozy experience for his girlfriend.<br>It was a warm, isolated wood cabin on the snowy alps. With a chill-out music playing on the background, a nice place to say for a while...<br>... if not by a system bug on the basement, showing a hidden path to another world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/776c714a27a3b284b264abf22ce4794d.poster.avif?t=1730629913\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/776c714a27a3b284b264abf22ce4794d.webm?t=1730629913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/776c714a27a3b284b264abf22ce4794d.mp4?t=1730629913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>On Fida Puti Samurai, you will incarnate as Liza, digging through a silly kind of rabbit hole:<br><br>- Traverse urban environments<br>- Visit 13 levels on urban settings<br>- Fight bunny-suit zombies, semi-naked waifus, punk gurls and others on 4 different enemy factions<br>- Use a wide variety of weapons from sledgehammers to dynamite and even panty-drying miniguns<br>- Discover the ability to transform into a Mahou Shoujo<br>- Uncover the secrets that lie on Zanardi's computer and his past<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/06b7d1791531c3eaf1d4ea93cd9d9650.poster.avif?t=1730629913\" width=602 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/06b7d1791531c3eaf1d4ea93cd9d9650.webm?t=1730629913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/06b7d1791531c3eaf1d4ea93cd9d9650.mp4?t=1730629913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/437683f3d6da638f321ca17e9bd690c6.poster.avif?t=1730629913\" width=586 height=586 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/437683f3d6da638f321ca17e9bd690c6.webm?t=1730629913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534340/extras/437683f3d6da638f321ca17e9bd690c6.mp4?t=1730629913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
